<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Root does not last for up to 8 ticks.LoL.A tick is a second,as shown in rain spells which have 3-4 ticks.Root lasts for a random duration,depending on your intel/skill VS monsters MR.And I use root at lev 17.Throw a root right off the bat,then throw 6-7 -120 DDs.Most things are tost by the 5th,cept for Beetles,which like to resist.<BR>
-Hobono</font></td></tr></table>
